  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Peace and Reconciliation Environments</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project expands the coverage that has been achieved within the framework of the Comprehensive Reintegration in Productive Environments project in Colombia, previously implemented by IOM and UNDP, and also incorporates good practices and lessons learned from the implementation of different reincorporation initiatives, specifically those related to the mainstreaming of the gender and community approach, the effective incorporation of environmental risk management, the leverage of the commercialization of products and services from the national level, and the capabilities strengthening of former FARC-EP combatants and their cooperatives to provide services in the productive lines that they have been developing.</narrative>
  </description>
